{
  "stem": "26465.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I remember my-- the friend from-- from-- from the trip-- she had this very beautiful long hair, down to her [INAUDIBLE]-- lower back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she was so desperate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She wanted to take her life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she was so upset about having her hair shaven.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She was-- she was so proud-- probably very proud of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And quite a lot of women were in a terrible, terrible predicament.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We only had-- the only contact we had-- when we were going for our soup-- for our soup-- daily food, and when our lineup met their lineup-- like, the barrack that their barracks was following-- and they were just joining our lineup, then we were talking.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the ladies there were-- most of them were very emaciated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very, very-- almost finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very lean, with hardly any-- any fat on them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just bones-- sheer bones sticking out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I believe they had been there for a longer period of time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they could hardly talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When they were saying something, it was so quiet that you would have to strain your ears to-- to listen to them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And quite a lot of them-- they were so courageous, in spite of it all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I noticed that one helped the other, and-- and they were saying-- I heard-- overheard-- the were of Polish origin-- they were saying, for example, [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That means, [INAUDIBLE], wait-- wait.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You will-- you will-- you will survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You will manage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You will manage, somehow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were giving each other the courage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The thing was that, later-- the later-- the later, towards our-- towards my going away from that camp, I noticed that that lineup was shorter and shorter and shorter.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then there was another influx of new women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And what happened to them, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
